# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:30
translate spanish hwb_s06_0764eba2:

    # "It feels like the page is staring back at me."
    "Siento que la página me devuelve la mirada."

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:32
translate spanish hwb_s06_5bfd6271:

    # "In fact, at this point, it probably is."
    "De hecho, a estas alturas, probablemente lo hace."

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:37
translate spanish hwb_s06_045aeaa7:

    # "My gaze drifts from the journal to the window by the entrance. Marina is outside, twirling the payphone's cord as she pops in another quarter."
    "Mi mirada se desvía del diario hacia la ventana de la entrada. Marina está afuera, girando el cable del teléfono público mientras mete otra moneda de veinticinco centavos."

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:41
translate spanish hwb_s06_90c89e34:

    # "She bites her lips and looks through the window. Our eyes meet. She sends me a small, anxious wave."
    "Se muerde los labios y mira a través de la ventana. Nuestras miradas se encuentran. Me envía un pequeño saludo ansioso con la mano."

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:45
translate spanish hwb_s06_5d07911b:

    # "Closing the book, I let out a yawn and remove my head from my fist. I'm sure there's a red imprint on my cheek."
    "Al cerrar el libro, bostezo y retiro la cabeza de mi puño. Seguro tengo una marca roja en la mejilla."

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:49
translate spanish hwb_s06_b5e512a0:

    # "Figuring out we had to go to Shiprock was the easy part. Everything else has been a gigantic pain the ass."
    "Descubrir que teníamos que ir a Shiprock fue la parte fácil. Todo lo demás ha sido un dolor de cabeza enorme."

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:58
translate spanish hwb_s06_d72b495b:

    # "There's a rush of precious cold air getting sucked from the building. Marina enters, carefully shutting the door, and taking the seat opposite me in the booth."
    "Una ráfaga de aire precioso y frío es succionada del edificio. Marina entra, cierra la puerta con cuidado y toma el asiento frente a mí en la cabina."

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:60
translate spanish hwb_s06_40918696:

    # Amber "So how'd it go?"
    Amber "Ну и как прошло?"

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:62
translate spanish hwb_s06_36eca0c0:

    # Marina "It went fine, I guess."
    Marina "Думаю, неплохо."

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:66
translate spanish hwb_s06_bfd624df:

    # Amber "Your parents are okay with all of this?"
    Amber "Твои родители нормально относятся ко всему этому?"

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:70
translate spanish hwb_s06_1cd454d1:

    # Marina "Maybe not \"okay...\""
    Marina "Ну, может и не совсем “нормально...”."

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:76
translate spanish hwb_s06_c70cf78d:

    # "A smile creeps onto her face."
    "Una sonrisa se dibuja lentamente en su rostro."

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:78
translate spanish hwb_s06_ee8e1501:

    # Marina "But they understand."
    Marina "Но они все понимают."

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:82
translate spanish hwb_s06_8ffd6259:

    # "At least someone gets it, because I still don't."
    "Al menos alguien lo entiende, porque yo todavía no."

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:86
translate spanish hwb_s06_77880ce1:

    # Marina "They weren't happy about the car, though."
    Marina "Правда пропажа машины их не обрадовала."

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:90
translate spanish hwb_s06_090013ca:

    # Amber "I think you were the only person who was."
    Amber "Думаю, ты была единственная, кого это обрадовало."

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:94
translate spanish hwb_s06_b96afb8a:

    # Marina "How couldn’t I be! Mariah showed us that the treasure is real!"
    Marina "Как я могла не обрадоваться! Мария доказала нам, что сокровище правда существует!"

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:98
translate spanish hwb_s06_3adec2e0:

    # Amber "You're going to believe the people who stole your car?"
    Amber "Ты готова поверить людям, которые угнали твою машину?"

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:102
translate spanish hwb_s06_5dad0f66:

    # Marina "{cps=80}I-{w=0.2}It was an accident! {w=0.4}They didn't mean to{/cps}{cps=3}...{/cps}"
    Marina "{cps=80}Э-{w=0.2}это была случайность!{w=0.4} Они не хотели этого{/cps}{cps=3}...{/cps}"

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:106
translate spanish hwb_s06_07290dde:

    # Marina "Besides, they're nice."
    Marina "К тому же они приятные люди."

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:110
translate spanish hwb_s06_caa538e6:

    # "Before I can argue further, our waitress emerges from the kitchen, carrying our order: a hot black coffee for me, a milkshake for Marina and a large order of fries for us both."
    "Antes de que pueda discutir más, nuestra mesera sale de la cocina, trayendo nuestro pedido: un café negro caliente para mí, un batido para Marina y una orden grande de papas fritas para ambas."

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:114
translate spanish hwb_s06_7e5b65d7:

    # "Marina's eyes brighten at the sight of the shake. Like with the slushie, her sweet tooth takes control of her and she practically starts drooling over the glass."
    "Los ojos de Marina se iluminan al ver el batido. Como con el raspado, su gusto por lo dulce la domina y prácticamente empieza a babear sobre el vaso."

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:116
translate spanish hwb_s06_2cee1206:

    # "With a nod, the waitress disappears back into the kitchen."
    "Con un asentimiento, la mesera desaparece de vuelta en la cocina."

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:120
translate spanish hwb_s06_a421ebe3:

    # Marina "Thanks for the food, by the way."
    Marina "Спасибо, кстати, что угощаешь."

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:124
translate spanish hwb_s06_9265b2d8:

    # Amber "Well, it's not like I really had a choice. I could hear your stomach from the driver's seat. I wasn't about to let you starve to death on my watch."
    Amber "Ну, не то чтобы у меня был выбор. Я слышала урчание твоего желудка даже с водительского места. Я не собиралась давать тебе умереть с голода в мою смену."

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:128
translate spanish hwb_s06_c784ca87:

    # Amber "Plus I was getting pretty hungry, too."
    Amber "К тому же я тоже неплохо проголодалась."

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:130
translate spanish hwb_s06_d3c4f042:

    # "Amazingly, Marina didn't freak out at the sight of the diner, like she has at everything else so far."
    "Sorprendentemente, Marina no se asustó al ver la cafetería, como ha hecho con todo lo demás hasta ahora."

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:132
translate spanish hwb_s06_c632baa3:

    # "I was genuinely shocked when I didn't hear a gasp of awe escape her mouth as we pulled up."
    "Me sorprendió de verdad no escuchar un jadeo de asombro salir de su boca cuando llegamos."

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:136
translate spanish hwb_s06_ba202d96:

    # Marina "Hey Amber, why don't you get a shake, too? Coffee and fries don't really go together, don't you think?"
    Marina "Слушай, Эмбер, почему бы тебе тоже не заказать коктейль? Кофе и картошка фри как-то не очень сочетаются, тебе не кажется?"

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:140
translate spanish hwb_s06_898e9046:

    # Amber "I'm fine. I don't really like sweet things."
    Amber "Для меня в самый раз. Я не очень-то люблю сладкое."

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:144
translate spanish hwb_s06_d9c1f122:

    # Marina "But it's super good. Especially when you dip your fries in it."
    Marina "Но коктейль просто невероятно вкусный. Особенно если макнуть туда картошку."

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:148
translate spanish hwb_s06_5a804887:

    # "She takes several of the fries and does just that, dipping them in the shake like it was ketchup or mustard."
    "Toma varias de las papas fritas y hace exactamente eso, sumergiéndolas en el batido como si fuera kétchup o mostaza."

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:152
translate spanish hwb_s06_f083efd2:

    # Amber "That’s silly. I can do the same thing with my coffee."
    Amber "Это глупо. Я могу и с кофе так же сделать."

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:156
translate spanish hwb_s06_82cb62bb:

    # "Taking a fry, I dunk it into my coffee and take a bite out of it."
    "Tomando una papa frita, la sumerjo en mi café y le doy un mordisco."

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:158
translate spanish hwb_s06_57420175:

    # "{cps=3}...{w=4.0}{nw}{/cps}"
    "{cps=3}...{w=4.0}{nw}{/cps}"

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:163
translate spanish hwb_s06_9c1d2061:

    # "That was a bad idea."
    "Esa fue una mala idea."

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:165
translate spanish hwb_s06_525d495e:

    # "Grimacing, I place the rest of the fry on my napkin as I try to cope with the cold chill and sulfury aftertaste."
    "Haciendo una mueca, coloco el resto de la papa frita en mi servilleta mientras intento lidiar con el escalofrío frío y el regusto sulfuroso."

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:169
translate spanish hwb_s06_de90b2e6:

    # Marina "Maybe it would work better if you put creamer in it?"
    Marina "Может будет лучше, если добавить сливок?"

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:173
translate spanish hwb_s06_3327d192:

    # Amber "Somehow, I doubt that. Besides, it would just ruin the coffee."
    Amber "Что-то сомневаюсь. К тому же это испортит кофе."

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:177
translate spanish hwb_s06_3d46900c:

    # Marina "I don’t know how you can even drink it without cream, or at least a little sugar. It’s so bitter."
    Marina "Не понимаю, как ты вообще можешь пить кофе без сливок, или без хотя бы ложечки сахара."

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:181
translate spanish hwb_s06_a6038ea8:

    # Amber "It’s an acquired taste. You find flavor in the bitterness."
    Amber "Вкус достаточно специфический, любовь к нему  приходит постепенно. Горечь кофе начинает казаться ароматной."

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:183
translate spanish hwb_s06_937acaed:

    # Marina "That’s why I think it’s weird that you drink something like that."
    Marina "Поэтому, я думаю, это странно, что ты пьешь нечто подобное."

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:187
translate spanish hwb_s06_f2200db7:

    # Amber "How do you mean?"
    Amber "Что ты имеешь в виду?"

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:191
translate spanish hwb_s06_bfaf41be:

    # Marina "I dunno…"
    Marina "Не знаю…"

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:193
translate spanish hwb_s06_f6dd9c35:

    # "Her brow furrows in deep thought."
    "Ella frunce el ceño en señal de profunda reflexión."

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:195
translate spanish hwb_s06_f3fcc916:

    # Marina "You always seem so… yes or no about stuff."
    Marina "Просто к таким вещам… ты как будто всегда относишься слишком определенно."

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:197
translate spanish hwb_s06_887fafa7:

    # Marina "If you like something, then you do. If you don’t like something, then you don’t."
    Marina "Если тебе что-то нравится, значит, тебе нравится. А если ты что-то не любишь, то не любишь."

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:199
translate spanish hwb_s06_810e13aa:

    # Amber "You’re losing me, Mare."
    Amber "Я не совсем тебя понимаю, Мари."

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:203
translate spanish hwb_s06_be3154a6:

    # Marina "What did Mom use to tell us when we didn’t listen to her…?"
    Marina "Помнишь что мамы обычно говорили нам, когда мы их не слушали…?"

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:207
translate spanish hwb_s06_ebd342b6:

    # Marina "Oh yeah!"
    Marina "Ах, да!"

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:211
translate spanish hwb_s06_c4b7c990:

    # Marina "Basically, you have a really thick head, Amber!"
    Marina "В общем, ты та еще тупица, Эмбер!"

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:215
translate spanish hwb_s06_ee84d831:

    # "I nearly spit the coffee out of my mouth."
    "Casi escupo el café de mi boca."

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:219
translate spanish hwb_s06_db472ede:

    # Amber "Gee, thanks."
    Amber "Вот же спасибо."

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:223
translate spanish hwb_s06_7dbd070e:

    # Marina "Or was it a thick skull?"
    Marina "Или там было “толстолобая”?"

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:227
translate spanish hwb_s06_b50db25b:

    # Marina "Whatever, you know what I mean, right?"
    Marina "В общем, какая разница, ты же понимаешь, что я имею в виду, да?"

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:231
translate spanish hwb_s06_c9997c23:

    # Amber "I think so. Maybe."
    Amber "Думаю да. Наверное."

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:235
translate spanish hwb_s06_f4a5f86f:

    # Amber "It wasn’t really an acquired taste for me, now that I think about it. Maybe I’ve always liked the bitterness."
    Amber "Наверное для меня он не такой уж специфический. Может быть, мне всегда нравился горький вкус."

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:237
translate spanish hwb_s06_c5e5af83:

    # "Or maybe I just convinced myself that I did. I don’t know."
    "O tal vez solo me convencí de que lo hice. No lo sé."

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:241
translate spanish hwb_s06_e55c454b:

    # Amber "Is that a bad thing?"
    Amber "Это плохо?"

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:245
translate spanish hwb_s06_a6a6579d:

    # "Just like in Mariah’s RV, Marina shakes her head and gives me a sweet, genuine smile."
    "Igual que en la casa rodante de Mariah, Marina niega con la cabeza y me dedica una sonrisa dulce y genuina."

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:247
translate spanish hwb_s06_fd86960a:

    # Marina "I don’t think so. I actually really like it. It reminds me of Shiprock."
    Marina "Я так не думаю. Мне это даже нравится. Напоминает о Шипроке."

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:251
translate spanish hwb_s06_89453a70:

    # "A warm tickling sensation bubbles up in my chest. It forces me to smile, but I play it off all cool and breezy like."
    "Una cálida sensación de cosquilleo burbujea en mi pecho. Me obliga a sonreír, pero lo disimulo con toda la frescura del mundo."

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:253
translate spanish hwb_s06_60f399bb:

    # Amber "Heh, I remind you of a rock? You shouldn't say that kinda thing. People might think they’re insults."
    Amber "Ха, я напоминаю тебе шипы? Не стоит говорить такие вещи. Люди могут подумать, что ты их оскорбляешь."

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:257
translate spanish hwb_s06_8da89276:

    # "Satisfied with how I played that off, I reach for a fry to reward myself, but instead of hot, crispy goodness, something smooth brushes against my fingertips."
    "Satisfecha con cómo lo manejé, busco una papa frita para recompensarme, pero en lugar de la bondad caliente y crujiente, algo suave roza mis yemas de los dedos."

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:259
translate spanish hwb_s06_36c9e17a:

    # "I gaze down at the plate of fries. Marina’s hand, for a split second, rests below mine."
    "Miro hacia abajo al plato de papas fritas. La mano de Marina, por una fracción de segundo, descansa debajo de la mía."

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:264
translate spanish hwb_s06_8d3c7e41:

    # "We instinctively snap back. Marina’s face is a bright shade of pink, and mine is probably similar."
    "Instintivamente nos separamos. La cara de Marina es de un tono rosa brillante, y la mía probablemente es similar."

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:266
translate spanish hwb_s06_a2f95924:

    # Amber "S-Sorry."
    Amber "Из-извини."

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:271
translate spanish hwb_s06_06bd0a08:

    # "The room feels ten degrees hotter. We try to re-establish eye contact, but our glances shoot off in other directions as soon as we meet."
    "La habitación se siente diez grados más caliente. Intentamos retomar el contacto visual, pero nuestras miradas se desvían en otras direcciones tan pronto como nos encontramos."

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:277
translate spanish hwb_s06_56bc22cb:

    # Marina "Hey, Amber…"
    Marina "Эй, Эмбер…"

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:281
translate spanish hwb_s06_2c934968:

    # "I manage to compose myself long enough to look back."
    "Logro recomponerme el tiempo suficiente para mirar de nuevo."

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:283
translate spanish hwb_s06_1e184984:

    # Marina "You said something about bills and expenses last night, right?"
    Marina "Ты что-то говорила про счета и расходы прошлой ночью, так?"

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:285
translate spanish hwb_s06_983bf5e4:

    # Marina "I don’t know what you exactly meant by that or what it is you have to pay off, but since we know the treasure is real now, I was wondering…"
    Marina "Не знаю, что именно ты имела в виду, или, что тебе нужно оплатить, но так как мы знаем, что сокровище правда есть, то я подумала…"

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:289
translate spanish hwb_s06_176348c8:

    # Marina "Maybe you might think about sticking around to look with me? We could even split it… or something."
    Marina "Может быть, ты бы подумала о том, чтобы послоняться и поискать его вместе со мной? Мы бы даже могли, ну... поделить его."

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:294
translate spanish hwb_s06_5c76c6cf:

    # Amber "W-Well, first off, we don’t even know if the treasure is actually real. Mariah could be pulling our legs."
    Amber "Ну, эм, во-первых, мы даже не знаем, правда ли существует это сокровище. Мария могла нас просто одурачить."

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:296
translate spanish hwb_s06_fec12884:

    # "My coffee is mostly gone. All that’s left is a puddle and a few stray grounds."
    "Mi café está casi terminado. Solo queda un charco y algunos posos sueltos."

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:298
translate spanish hwb_s06_f7c7b5e3:

    # Amber "I’ll think about it, though."
    Amber "Но я подумаю над этим."

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:302
translate spanish hwb_s06_cee675b3:

    # Marina "Really?"
    Marina "Правда?"

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:306
translate spanish hwb_s06_7a6e9b4f:

    # Amber "I only said I would think about it! Don’t get too excited just yet!"
    Amber "Я только сказала, что подумаю над этим! Не радуйся раньше времени!"

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:310
translate spanish hwb_s06_4d5e5b40:

    # Marina "I won’t, I won’t. I just think it would be super cool."
    Marina "Не буду, не буду. Я просто думаю, что это будет невероятно круто."

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:312
translate spanish hwb_s06_dcd9185e:

    # "Marina flops her chin down and rests on the table."
    "Marina deja caer la barbilla y se apoya en la mesa."

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:316
translate spanish hwb_s06_50bb5903:

    # Marina "How’s it going anyway? Have you figured out where the first part of the treasure might be?"
    Marina "А как вообще с этим идут дела? Ты выяснила, где может быть первая часть сокровища?"

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:320
translate spanish hwb_s06_1e76f8b8:

    # Amber "No luck."
    Amber "Пока нет."

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:322
translate spanish hwb_s06_fa744223:

    # Amber "It’s not like the guy drew a map or anything. He just jotted down details about the places he went to."
    Amber "Это не тот случай, когда парень нарисовал карту или что-то типа того. Он просто кратко записал детали о местах, в которых побывал."

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:324
translate spanish hwb_s06_28874353:

    # "That, and rambling about how awesome he was."
    "Eso, y divagando sobre lo increíble que era."

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:328
translate spanish hwb_s06_815b6873:

    # Marina "Do you think Mariah was right and he hid it on top of ol’ Shippy?"
    Marina "Думаешь, Мария была права, и он спрятал его на вершине горы Шиппи?"

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:332
translate spanish hwb_s06_062d7324:

    # Amber "Don’t listen to Mariah, okay? She doesn’t know what she’s talking about."
    Amber "Не слушай Марию, ладно? Она не знает, о чем говорит."

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:336
translate spanish hwb_s06_d6cd02fc:

    # Amber "Think about it—how would he even scale the mountain? He was traveling solo on horseback. I doubt he would have the tools to do it."
    Amber "Подумай – как бы он вообще забрался на ту гору? Он путешествовал в одиночку на лошади. Сомневаюсь, что у него было снаряжение для такого подъема."

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:340
translate spanish hwb_s06_d23c7245:

    # Amber "And even if he did, I’m pretty sure he would’ve gone on and on about it in his journal."
    Amber "Да даже если и вправду забрался. Я больше чем уверена, он исписал бы каждую страницу дневника о таком восхождении."

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:342
translate spanish hwb_s06_a6192f93:

    # "With a puppy-dog whine, Marina frowns."
    "Con un quejido de cachorrito, Marina frunce el ceño."

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:344
translate spanish hwb_s06_4385b5ec:

    # Marina "Are you sure he didn’t mention anything else? Maybe something we didn’t catch."
    Marina "Ты уверена, что он не написал что-нибудь еще? Может что-то, что мы упустили."

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:348
translate spanish hwb_s06_3caea829:

    # "I slide the book across the table and over the leftover crumbs, stretching out my stiff joints as I rest against the booth."
    "Deslizo el libro a través de la mesa y sobre las migajas sobrantes, estirando mis articulaciones rígidas mientras me recuesto contra la cabina."

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:350
translate spanish hwb_s06_7a143c03:

    # Amber "Take a look, if you want. My eyes are gonna start bleeding if I read it again."
    Amber "Вот, посмотри, если хочешь. Из моих глаз пойдет кровь, если я снова начну читать это."

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:352
translate spanish hwb_s06_3ad68708:

    # Amber "The only things he really mentioned are the rocks and the dikes around it."
    Amber "Совершенно прямо он указал лишь на скалы и окружающие их дайки."

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:356
translate spanish hwb_s06_10c1378e:

    # Marina "O-Oh."
    Marina "Оох."

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:358
translate spanish hwb_s06_494806be:

    # "Marina forces herself to stare down at the plate, the blush from earlier reappearing."
    "Marina se obliga a mirar fijamente el plato, el rubor de antes reapareciendo."

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:362
translate spanish hwb_s06_719cd64b:

    # "‘Oh?’"
    "‘¿Oh?’"

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:377
translate spanish hwb_s06_7464f6b5:

    # "{cps=4}Ohhhhhhhhh.{/cps}"
    "{cps=4}Ooooooooh.{/cps}"

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:382
translate spanish hwb_s06_f520dfa7:

    # Amber "No, not like that."
    Amber "Нет, не ох."

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:386
translate spanish hwb_s06_d94ebad0:

    # "I stifle a giggle. Teasing her is gonna be a blast."
    "Ahogo una risita. Burlarme de ella va a ser divertidísimo."

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:390
translate spanish hwb_s06_7a5b8836:

    # Amber "I mean the rocks that branch out from the mountain. That’s what they’re call—"
    Amber "Я имею в виду скалы, которые отходят от горы. Вот, они называ—"

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:396
translate spanish hwb_s06_e6af55bb:

    # Amber "Huh."
    Amber "Хм."

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:400
translate spanish hwb_s06_9a997626:

    # "It’s so simple. But it makes sense."
    "Es tan simple. Pero tiene sentido."

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:402
translate spanish hwb_s06_59a2a38b:

    # "I shoot up and throw down some money. Marina jumps at the sound of the table rattling."
    "Me levanto de un salto y dejo caer algo de dinero. Marina da un brinco al oír el sonido de la mesa temblar."

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:406
translate spanish hwb_s06_62af7cff:

    # Marina "What’s the matter? Did you figure out where it is?"
    Marina "Что случилось? Ты поняла, где он?"

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:410
translate spanish hwb_s06_7a19533e:

    # Amber "Maybe. At least a general area."
    Amber "Возможно. По крайней мере, примерное местоположение."

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:416
translate spanish hwb_s06_e18e38ec:

    # "I march towards the door."
    "Marcho hacia la puerta."

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:418
translate spanish hwb_s06_bd6c7bb9:

    # "The table rattles again as Marina leaps up. She stays behind to straighten it out before scrambling to catch up with me."
    "La mesa vuelve a temblar cuando Marina salta. Se queda atrás para enderezarla antes de apresurarse a alcanzarme."

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:422
translate spanish hwb_s06_32c592e8:

    # Marina "We’re going now?"
    Marina "И что, мы прямо сейчас отправляемся?"

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:424
translate spanish hwb_s06_3052415b:

    # Amber "Hell no. We don’t have any equipment."
    Amber "Черт возьми, нет. У нас нет подходящего оборудования."

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:429
translate spanish hwb_s06_3a355c72:

    # Amber "But we know someone who does."
    Amber "Но мы знаем того, у кого оно есть."

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:436
translate spanish hwb_s06_92172216:

    # "I shove the door open, the last bastion between refreshing air and burning, dry heat."
    "Empujo la puerta para abrirla, el último bastión entre el aire fresco y el calor ardiente y seco."

# game/script/hwb_s06.rpy:440
translate spanish hwb_s06_a8c45e26:

    # Amber "C’mon, let’s go cash in a favor."
    Amber "Пойдем, вернем должок."

